  "prompt": "What should I do to make life worth living?",
  "response": "Here are some suggestions for finding meaning and fulfillment in life:\n\n1. Personal Growth\n- Set meaningful goals\n- Learn continuously\n- Develop skills\n- Challenge yourself\n\n2. Relationships\n- Cultivate deep connections\n- Be kind and supportive\n- Spend time with loved ones\n- Build a supportive community\n\n3. Purpose\n- Find work or activities that inspire you\n- Contribute to something larger than yourself\n- Help others\n- Pursue your passions\n\n4. Mental Health\n- Practice self-care\n- Manage stress\n- Develop resilience\n- Seek therapy if needed\n\n5. Physical Well-being\n- Exercise regularly\n- Eat nutritious food\n- Get enough sleep\n- Practice mindfulness\n\n6. Experiences\n- Travel\n- Try new things\n- Create memories\n- Step out of your comfort zone\n\n7. Personal Values\n- Define your core values\n- Live authentically\n- Make choices aligned with your beliefs\n\n8. Gratitude\n- Appreciate what you have\n- Practice daily gratitude\n- Focus on positive aspects of life\n\nRemember, meaning is personal and can be different for everyone. Explore what resonates with you and create a life that feels fulfilling and authentic.",
